@{b}S3Host@{ub}
******

   This document describes the use of the @{b}S3Host@{ub} program, a utility to
simplify file transfers between @{b}Amiga@{ub} and @{b}Psion S3@{ub} and @{b}S3a@{ub} palmtop
computers.

   @{b}S3Host@{ub} is (C) 1994 Oliver Wagner, All Rights Reserved.


